g outputs.
Most fields in the natural sciences don=E2=80=99t have Internet-scale data,=
 or anywhere close to it. At the London-based AI research lab DeepMind, Dem=
is Hassabis was acutely aware of this challenge. With a background as a chi=
ld chess prodigy, game developer, and academic neuroscientist (seriously), =
Hassabis had built DeepMind into a world-class AI lab. After his team built=
