=2Ecom/redirect/abe793fe-ddd5-488c-b87f-1=
5aff4f31788?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.g=
b8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].=C2=A0
Being able to predict the structure of proteins is a=C2=A0 big deal for bio=
technology. As we=E2=80=99ve seen, there is a deep connection between struc=
ture and function in biology. With these models, it=E2=80=99s now possible =
to explore the total space of protein structures on a scale that was previo=
usly unimaginable [ https://substack.com/redirect/86f46ed0-58e2-42aa-8a23-2=
7da755ba970?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkR=
NpU ]. In this renaissance, approaches to designing proteins with entirely =
