accines=E2=80=94have also dramatically improved. This massive step change i=
n modeling has been said [ https://substack.com/redirect/312cbc30-c3e2-4589=
-b5c5-b97569728079?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-=
6m8ExkRNpU ] to be =E2=80=9C=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8Btransforming the field of bio=
molecular structure prediction and design.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
Structure leads to function, and new understanding of structures leads to n=
