Based on the success of AI for a problem as challenging as structure predic=
tion, Hassabis articulated [ https://substack.com/redirect/7011cb40-d79f-49=
0f-87e0-0b1188ca2b46?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa=
8-6m8ExkRNpU ] a compelling vision for the future at the intersection of AI=
