> Atoms. The most impactful progress will come at the </span><strong>inters=
ection of Bits </strong><em><strong>and</strong></em><strong> Atoms</strong=
><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Atomic AI</strong><span> is a pe=
rfect case study. Atoms and Bits are right there in the name.&#160;</span><=
/p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
