40; text-decoration: underline;">produces</a><span> north of $500 billion i=
n annual revenue in the U.S. alone&#8212;is a result of this paradigm shift=
=2E</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040;=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
