lated</a><span> a compelling vision for the future at the intersection of A=
I and biology:</span></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #67bdf=
c; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px=
; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><span>At i=
ts most fundamental level, I think biology can be thought of as an informat=
